rol cố gắng tìm ra vị trí của mình sau khi được thăng chức. Tại Berkeley, Rachel đấu tranh để cân bằng đạo đức của mình với chủ nghĩa tư bản, trong khi Brad sau khi ra tù cố gắng trở lại xã hội như một người đàn ông đã cải tạo.</p>","tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"94951","season":3,"vote_average":7.259,"vote_count":424},"modified":"2024-08-18T07:44:51.000Z","cast":["Rob Mac","Charlotte Nicdao","Ashly Burch","Naomi Ekperigin","Jessie Ennis","Imani Hakim","Danny Pudi","David Hornsby"],"director":[],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Rob Mac","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Rob Mac","tmdb_id":78597,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/gcep3ItyxaZ3ljH1IS6Lfkm8IAs.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/78597"},{"name":"Charlotte Nicdao","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Charlotte Nicdao","tmdb_id":1434826,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/rCqf3HcEr4GmSYAMqmdEpo6cZwr.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1434826"},{"name":"Ashly Burch","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Ashly Burch","tmdb_id":1156183,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/iINzNKiIGbjoee6tJKb8xMWog45.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1156183"},{"name":"Naomi Ekperigin","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Naomi Ekperigin","tmdb_id":1974164,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hWYaQf5kZuZvRd0CHxELh2V6rhs.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1974164"},{"name":"Jessie Ennis","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Jessie Ennis","tmdb_id":1569001,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/Rx6zznL7EVBuOueSPfsuPlPvun.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1569001"},{"name":"Imani Hakim","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Imani Hakim","tmdb_id":202850,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ccau9npD8M3r1LDdr17lgFzPT0W.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/202850"},{"name":"Danny Pudi","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Danny Pudi","tmdb_id":205179,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/w0zT8Y2dQHU8FgV03NJoHJE6tmD.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.th